-- Curro Doubles Target to 80 Schools by 2022, Financial Mail Says
-- B y   S i k o n a t h i   M a n t s h a n t s h a
-- 2012-06-28T12:58:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/curro-doubles-target-to-80-schools-by-2022-financial-mail-says.html
Curro Holdings Ltd. (COH)  could have 80
private schools in its network by 2022, double the amount it
expected to achieve by 2020, the  Financial Mail  said, citing
Chief Executive Officer Chris van Der Merwe.  The company plans to have 26 schools with 16,000 learners
during financial 2013, the Johannesburg-based magazine said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
